\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\mathrm{D}f(u)=\mathrm{J}_{f}(u):=\begin{pmatrix}(\partial_{x_{1}}f_{1})(u) & \cdots & (\partial_{x_{m}}f_{1})(u)\\
\vdots & \ddots & \vdots\\
(\partial_{x_{1}}f_{n})(u) & \cdots & (\partial_{x_{m}}f_{n})(u)
\end{pmatrix}.
\]

\end_inset

Indeed, suppose 
\begin_inset Formula $h=(0,\dots,h_{i},\dots,0)^{\top}$
\end_inset

 and let 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathrm{D}f(u)_{i}$
\end_inset

 (respectively 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathrm{\mathrm{D}}f(u)_{i}^{j})$
\end_inset

